article.headline: Ingraham scores 16 in Rider's 64-53 win over Coppin State
article.description: — Tariq Ingraham scored 16 points as Rider beat Coppin State 64-53 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Ingraham scores 16 in Rider's 64-53 win over Coppin State
article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Tariq Ingraham scored 16 points as Rider beat Coppin State 64-53 on Saturday. Ingraham had nine rebounds and three blocks for the Broncs (2-1). TJ Weeks Jr. added 12 points while going 2 of 7 from the floor, including 2 for 6 from 3-point range, and 6 for 6 from the line while he also had seven rebounds. Aasim Burton shot 4 of 7 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line to finish with 11 points. Derrius Ward and Toby Nnadozie each scored 18 points for the Eagles (0-3). ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
